cu_modifications.explanation: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF to the same IP as the AMF (192.168.70.132) creates an IP conflict, preventing proper NG interface binding and causing AMF connection failure.
cu_modifications.explanation_zh: 將 GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF 設定為與 AMF 相同的 IP (192.168.70.132) 會造成 IP 衝突，阻止正確的 NG 接口綁定，並導致 AMF 連接失敗。

du_modifications.explanation: Setting absoluteFrequencySSB to 0, which is below the valid frequency range, will cause SSB transmission failure and prevent UE synchronization.
du_modifications.explanation_zh: 將 absoluteFrequencySSB 設定為 0，低於有效頻率範圍，會導致 SSB 傳輸失敗，並阻止 UE 同步。
